38343>>>>>        Else Begin
38344>>>>>            WebSet pbRender of oSaveBtn to True
38345>>>>>            WebSet pbRender of oCancelChangesBtn to True
38346>>>>>            WebSet pbRender of oDeleteBtn to bHasRecord
38347>>>>>        End
38347>>>>>>
38347>>>>>    End_Procedure
