38464>>>    Procedure OnNavigateForward tWebNavigateData NavigateData Integer hoInvokingView Integer hoInvokingObject //InvokingView: Invocamos la otra vista
38467>>>        WebSet pbRender of oNewButton to True
38468>>>        WebSet pbRender of oDetailButton to True
38469>>>
38469>>>        Case Begin
38469>>>            Case (NavigateData.eNavigateType = nfFromParent)
38471>>>                // If from parent, this is a constrained drill down
